# http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/creator
<http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/creator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#AnnotationProperty> .
