# http://purl.org/emmedi/hico/InterpretationAct
<http://purl.org/emmedi/hico/InterpretationAct> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
# 
# http://w3id.org/opino/Assertion
<http://w3id.org/opino/Assertion> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Assertion> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass> _:genid1 .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
_:genid1 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#intersectionOf> _:genid4 .
_:genid4 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid2 .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#nil> .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> _:genid3 .
_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#hasValue> <http://w3id.org/opino/AssertionValue> .
_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://w3id.org/opino/hasEpistemicStatus> .
_:genid3 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
_:genid2 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
_:genid4 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> <http://w3id.org/opino/Opinion> .
_:genid4 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Assertion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An Opinion the holder commits to as their current considered interpretation, supported by evidence or argument they regard as sufficient to warrant commitment."@en .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Assertion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "http://w3id.org/opino/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Assertion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Assertion"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/opino/Conjecture
<http://w3id.org/opino/Conjecture> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Conjecture> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass> _:genid5 .
_:genid5 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
_:genid5 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#intersectionOf> _:genid8 .
_:genid8 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> _:genid6 .
_:genid6 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#nil> .
_:genid6 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> _:genid7 .
_:genid7 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#hasValue> <http://w3id.org/opino/ConjectureValue> .
_:genid7 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://w3id.org/opino/hasEpistemicStatus> .
_:genid7 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
_:genid6 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
_:genid8 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first> <http://w3id.org/opino/Opinion> .
_:genid8 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#List> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Conjecture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An Opinion held with minimal epistemic commitment, entertained as a possibility without sufficient evidence to assert it."@en .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Conjecture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "http://w3id.org/opino/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Conjecture> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Conjecture"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/opino/Construal
<http://w3id.org/opino/Construal> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Construal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Situation> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Construal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid9 .
_:genid9 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#allValuesFrom> <http://w3id.org/opino/Construal> .
_:genid9 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://w3id.org/opino/hasPart> .
_:genid9 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Construal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A situation constituted by the premises as perceived by the agent responsible for an Opinion. It is perspective-dependent — it reifies the state of affairs from the standpoint of the cognizer, not an objective state of affairs. A Construal can be composed of parts, each of which is itself a dul:Situation representing an individual premise (i.e., another state of affairs). The dul:Situation, part of the Construal, can be satisfied by a secondary dul:Description."@en .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Construal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "http://w3id.org/opino/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/Construal> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Construal"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicRegion
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicRegion> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicRegion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Region> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicRegion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A region in the epistemic quality space representing the degree of individual commitment an agent holds toward an Opinion. Three values are defined: ConjectureValue (speculative), HypothesisValue (tentative), AssertionValue (committed). Community-level reception is handled separately via CiTO properties on hico:InterpretationAct."@en .
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicRegion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "http://w3id.org/opino/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicRegion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Epistemic Region"@en .
# 
# http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicStatusParameter
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicStatusParameter> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicStatusParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Parameter> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicStatusParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> _:genid10 .
_:genid10 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onClass> <http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicRegion> .
_:genid10 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#qualifiedCardinality> "1"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger> .
_:genid10 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty> <http://w3id.org/opino/hasEpistemicRegion> .
_:genid10 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Restriction> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicStatusParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A parameter component of an Opinion that carries its epistemic status value. In DnS terms, this is a typed component of the Description that gets valued by a region in the epistemic quality space. Each Opinion has exactly one EpistemicStatusParameter at any given time."@en .
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicStatusParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> "http://w3id.org/opino/"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<http://w3id.org/opino/EpistemicStatusParameter> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Epistemic Status (Parameter)"@en .
# 
