<http://w3id.org/opino/Opinion> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A description, in the DnS sense, representing a claim held by an agent about an entity or state of affairs. An Opinion is satisfied by a Construal — the set of facts as perceived by the cognizer that grounds the claim. An Opinion is generated by a prov:Activity, which attributes it to the agent responsible for its production."@en .
